Hey everyone, I don’t know how to write this and never thought in a million years I would have to or asking for help... but here we are.... those that know me, know what my 2 wonderful girls mean to me, they are my life... 
Im heartbroken to say that Roka is facing some uncertainty with her health right now & is needing multiple vet visits due to a cancerous tumour we recently found.
But I am hopeful that with the help and support of my amazing friends, family & all of those around me that we can give Roka a chance for us to spend many more years together. 
Any shares would be greatly appreciated & of course your donations mean so much to me right now xxx Link is in bio for the go fund me I have created ❤️🐾❤️

Half back panel all fresh - john has a woman / spirit who protects him in life , although he has never seen her himself- those that have, say she wears a white dress with her dark hair up in a bun style… and is always seen over his shoulder … so he asked for me to represent this as a shoulder piece - but we changed to cover half the back for a nicer composition as either a stand alone piece or the option in the future to turn into a full back piece ..
